data.title: Journal of Education, Health and Sport
data.text:
The Institute of Health of the State Higher Vocational School, we have the honor to invite you to the Conference Scientific research entitled: "Health literacy as the challenge of the 21st century.

The thematic scope of the conference covers a number of important ones health issues and related challenges in the context of the COVID-19 pandemic. We are confident that each of you can make a valuable contribution to the discussion on issues falling within the program area Conference.

Scientific and Organizational Committee of the Conference

The conference 27-28 October 2022 in a hybrid form at the Didactic and Sports Campus of the State Higher Vocational School in Nowy Scz, ul. Kociuszki 2A.
